## What happened

I was debugging based on the lab https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/first-flutter-app-pt2/#6.
While the error was presented, it allowed the application to function normally. I stopped debugging when the error occurred.

## Version information

Android Studio `3.5.1` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 40.0.2` • Dart plugin `191.8423`

Flutter 1.9.1+hotfix.4 • channel stable • https://github.com/flutter/flutter.git
Framework • revision cc949a8e8b (hace 10 días) • 2019-09-27 15:04:59 -0700
Engine • revision b863200c37
Tools • Dart 2.5.0
